Whenever Slimefoot and Squee enters or attacks, create a 1/1 green Saproling creature token.
{1}{B}{R}{G}, Sacrifice a Saproling: Return this card and up to one other target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield. Activate only as a sorcery.

worldly tutor.name: Worldly Tutor
worldly tutor.oracle_text: Search your library for a creature card, reveal it, then shuffle and put the card on top.
worldly tutor.flavor_text: "All of us, from the tiny leaf-mite to the towering baloth, are vital threads in the weave of life."
